c: 59
v: 24
t: "Woh Allah hi hai, jo takhleeq( creation) ka mansuba(plan) banane wala, aur usko nafiz karne wala, aur uske mutabik surat-gari (fashioner) karne wala hai. Uske liye behtareen naam hain. Har cheez jo aasmano aur zameen mein hai uski tasbeeh kar rahi hai, aur woh zabardast aur Hakeem hai"